        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12702800/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12702800/" class="">第121页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/williampitt/" class=" " title="Favillae">Favillae</a>
                (S&#39;il plaît à dieu.)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12702800">
